Package: bankcheck
Type: Project
Title: Bank Check
Version: 1.0.0
Description: Dependency manifest for the Bank Check Shiny app. Not an R
    package; Imports below is the app's direct runtime dependency list,
    read by .github/workflows/deploy.yml, which installs it (plus
    dependencies) as binaries from a dated Posit Package Manager snapshot
    so tests and deploys see the same package versions every run.
    Deploy-only tooling (shinylive, rsconnect) is installed in the
    workflow from the same snapshot but deliberately left out of Imports.
Imports:
    shiny,
    bslib,
    plotly,
    dplyr,
    DT,
    commonmark,
    jsonlite,
    htmltools
